                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18180506-89-off497 t18180506-89-cd498"></join>, one staff tipped with silver, value 3l., the property of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18180506-89-victim790" type="victimName">
